Bartleby is rich, so rich in fact that he could choose anyone to be his bithc, yet he chooses sonic? the fat hedgehog? Sonic is a nobody. He's not anything special and he's worthless, but even then, bartleby can see something unique in Sonic that makes him stand out from the rest of the world, and that is sonic's love for bartleby. most people love bartleby for is money or his looks, but sonic... Sonic loves bartleby for who he is. And bartleby knows that. Who better to choose as your bitch than somebody who loves you for who you are and not for what you can buy?
